<p id="mwaA">As before, we can set <span class="mwe-math-element" id="mwaQ"><span class="mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style="display: none;"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" alttext="{\displaystyle t\equiv x^{0}}">
