<p id="mwsw">Multiplying by the inverse <a href="Metric_tensor" title="Metric tensor" id="mwtA">metric tensor</a> <span class="mwe-math-element" id="mwtQ"><span class="mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style="display: none;"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" alttext="{\displaystyle g^{\mu \beta }}">
