<p id="mw5A">with</p>

<dl id="mw5Q"><dd id="mw5g"><span class="mwe-math-element" id="mw5w"><span class="mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style="display: none;"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" alttext="{\displaystyle {\eta _{\alpha \beta }}{dX^{\alpha } \over ds}{dX^{\beta } \over ds}=-1.}">
