<p id="mw-Q">with</p>

<dl id="mw-g"><dd id="mw-w"><span class="mwe-math-element" id="mw_A"><span class="mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style="display: none;"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" alttext="{\displaystyle {g_{\alpha \beta }}{dx^{\alpha } \over ds}{dx^{\beta } \over ds}=-1.}">
