<p id="mwASA">where <span class="mwe-math-element" id="mwASE"><span class="mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style="display: none;"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" alttext="{\displaystyle U^{\mu }={\dot {x}}^{\mu }.}">
